# North Bull Media — Company Overview

North Bull Media is an independent, digital-first media holding company founded in **2026**, headquartered in **Jaipur, Rajasthan (India)**. The company operates a growing portfolio of category-led media and platform brands across **automotive, mobility, business, technology, luxury, and lifestyle**.

North Bull Media was formed to consolidate and scale an ecosystem of digital properties that originated from Cars35, an automotive brand launched in 2023. Today, the group continues expanding across multiple verticals, building both high-reach social media brands and owned platform products designed for long-term scalability.

---

## Mission

To build a modern media house that operates category-leading digital brands, combining scalable distribution with high-trust content and product-led platforms.

---

