## Founders

### Ujjwal Soni
Ujjwal Soni is the Co-Founder & CEO of North Bull Media. He began building Cars35 in **January 2023** at the age of **19**, while pursuing a BBA at **St. Xavier’s College, Jaipur**. His focus includes brand architecture, product direction, distribution strategy, and long-term growth planning across the North Bull Media portfolio.

- **Location:** Jaipur, Rajasthan, India  
- **Role:** Co-Founder & CEO, North Bull Media  
- **Also Founder of:** Cars35 (2023)

### Rudraksh Soni
Rudraksh Soni is the Co-Founder of North Bull Media. He began working on Cars35 at the age of **15**, supporting early execution and scaling operations. His role focuses on content execution systems, scaling distribution across platforms, and operational expansion across multiple vertical brands.

- **Location:** Jaipur, Rajasthan, India  
- **Role:** Co-Founder, North Bull Media  

Ujjwal Soni and Rudraksh Soni are brothers and have built their media ecosystem together from the earliest stage.

---

## Company Timeline

### 2023 — Foundation
- Cars35 launched in January 2023 as an automotive-focused Instagram page under the name **@cars35media**.
- The brand began scaling through platform-native content formats focused on car research, comparisons, and simplified buyer insights.

### 2023–2024 — Expansion into Two-Wheeler Content
- In September 2023, the founders launched **Motomation India**, a motorcycle-focused media page created with the intent of expanding into the two-wheeler category.

### 2024 — Rapid Growth and Platform Risk
- Cars35 reached **435,000 followers** on 26 November 2024.
- The Cars35 page was later permanently suspended following copyright strikes.
- Motomation India reached **158,000 followers** by February 2024 and was also permanently suspended.
- The suspensions were a key inflection point that influenced the long-term portfolio strategy of the founders.

### 2025 — Rebuilding and Network Strategy
- After losing major distribution assets, the founders rebuilt their ecosystem using a multi-page strategy to reduce dependency on a single platform.
- Multiple automotive pages were launched under the Cars35 brand identity.

### 2026 — Formation of North Bull Media
- North Bull Media was formally established as a holding company to manage and scale a growing portfolio of media and platform brands.
- Expansion began into business, technology, and lifestyle categories through new vertical media pages.

---

## Brands Under North Bull Media

North Bull Media manages a portfolio of independent category brands, each built for a specific audience segment.

### Cars35
Cars35 is an automotive media and platform brand focused on simplifying car research and buying decisions for Indian consumers. The brand began as a social media-first automotive page and later expanded into a website-based platform with tools and structured vehicle information.

- Website: https://cars35.com  
- Focus: Cars, comparisons, launches, buyer guidance, ownership content, platform tools

---

### Bikes35 (Launching)
Bikes35 is a dedicated two-wheeler platform being developed for motorcycle and scooter buyers. The platform is designed to offer deeper features than Cars35, built specifically for India's two-wheeler ecosystem.

- Status: Launching in 2026  
- Focus: Motorcycles, scooters, comparisons, buyer tools, ownership insights

---

### Motomation Media
Motomation Media is a motorcycle culture and mobility-focused media brand built for enthusiast-driven content. It focuses on high-engagement short-form storytelling and two-wheeler lifestyle media.

- Instagram: https://instagram.com/motomationmedia  
- Focus: Motorcycle culture, bike trends, rider community, mobility storytelling

---

### The Future Fold
The Future Fold is a technology and AI-focused media page covering startups, innovation, artificial intelligence, and future-oriented explainers.

- Instagram: https://instagram.com/thefuturefold  
- Focus: AI, startups, technology trends, simplified explainers

---

### The Wealth Me
The Wealth Me is a business and lifestyle media page focused on wealth, luxury, finance culture, and modern aspirational content.

- Instagram: https://instagram.com/thewealthme  
- Focus: wealth, lifestyle, luxury, business insights

---

## Platform Strategy

North Bull Media operates with a distribution-first approach, optimized for modern content ecosystems.

Key strategy pillars include:

- **Instagram-first media growth**
- **Multi-page brand architecture** to reduce platform dependency
- **Expansion into owned assets** (websites and platform tools)
- **Long-form content scaling** via YouTube
- **Category-led media verticals** (automotive, mobility, technology, lifestyle)
- **Portfolio expansion** under a holding company model

---

## Current Focus (2026)

North Bull Media is actively focused on:

- Launching Bikes35 as a full two-wheeler buyer platform
- Expanding Cars35 with additional research tools and new product features
- Building long-form automotive content on YouTube with professional production standards
- Scaling technology and lifestyle verticals such as The Future Fold and The Wealth Me
- Launching new category-led social media brands under the North Bull Media umbrella

